column5: Going to Minnitaki for the Canadian opener. Does Navionics cover Minnitaki? If not, how tough is it to navigate? Never been there. Any early tips on what tackle to bring. Walleyes, bass, pike, trout. Thanks in advance.
Don't believe so, at least not on the premium chip. See here > http://navionics.com/PremiumLakeList_06.asp?RegionID=5
